{"tid":1582070,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"轉貼 香港革命未來日記","createTime":"2019-09-20T01:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T03:23:25.000Z","uid":299702,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ac0e780f5f60f4c2eec7ac6164233a9eaa1b3118","tid":1582070,"uid":299702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T01:20:12.000Z","msg":"轉貼 未來日記<br />\n=============<br />\n<br />\n今日係2021年10月31日，係新香港政府成立既一周年紀念日，距香港革命完結已經一年多了。<br />\n<br />\n自從新政府停左每天150個新移民，現時香港大陸居民逐漸減少，社會亦逐漸回到安寧。<br />\n<br />\n回想起當年既革命尾聲<br />\n當香港人權法案過左後，中共開始同香港政府割席，當年既警察被中共下令全面清算，我諗d 警察真係諗都冇諗過，林鄭仲極速話警察已不受控，又強烈讉責不法既警務人員，真係令全港市民大跌眼鏡，可惜已經太遲。<br />\n<br />\n事後新屋巔陸續有警察流出絕密記錄，證明左公安和黑警起碼殺左20個香港示威者，其實個時咁多自殺案都知知地，但就係證實唔到。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰仲連開幾個記者會去澄清話絕無此事，可惜後來越黎越多警察出黎證實呢件事，個革命先得以結束。<br />\n<br />\n個陣時政府宣佈全面特赦，示威者全部無罪釋放，每次有人放出黎市民都大唱「願榮光歸香港」，真係感動唔少人。<br />\n<br />\n但黑警都特赦埋，唉。。。呢個可能係美中不足之處，雖然事後好多黑警都唔知點解係香港消失左。（送左返大陸？）<br />\n<br />\n今日亦係何妖既死忌，當年佢被發現伏屍在父母墳前，真係嚇左大家一跳，差d 又入埋黃絲數，如果唔係中聯辦出聲明話全部惡行都係何妖策劃，我諗佢仲可以玩多幾年既。<br />\n<br />\n回憶就到呢度啦，一陣去睇下一個 500萬500尺既單位先。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n========<br />\n我都好想呢個日記係真呀！大家要加油！"},{"pid":"2ea387d4f118d5d68cee29dd818b85d15e543501","tid":1582070,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T01:20:36.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581619</a><br />\n<br />\n【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊 - 會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人 - 食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8mVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=1176c8de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"b0a903d8c54c15635ae20d7a45fe58265c2869b0","tid":1582070,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T01:28:15.000Z","msg":"<strong>921 光復屯門</strong><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U5cMNwQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU5cMNwQ.jpg&h=236dcf53&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3vmqiHS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3vmqiHS.jpg&h=8258ecbb&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>9.28傘運五週年放映會</strong><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t4n5iHm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft4n5iHm.jpg&h=fab56cb8&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>9.29全球抗赤納粹集會</strong><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8VYswYv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8VYswYv.png&h=7f8aab5c&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>10.1全民黑衣日</strong><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cy9vuN1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcy9vuN1.jpg&h=482339c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2LysBS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2LysBS.jpg&h=f368412d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b30bd1c3f75a9ef2586c2c0f74b6974466c30e04","tid":1582070,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T01:34:46.000Z","msg":"<strong>921 光復屯門</strong><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U5cMNwQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU5cMNwQ.jpg&h=236dcf53&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3vmqiHS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3vmqiHS.jpg&h=8258ecbb&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>9.28傘運五週年放映會</strong><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t4n5iHm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft4n5iHm.jpg&h=fab56cb8&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>9.29全球抗赤納粹集